 means
(for U1,U2 being  strict (SubAlgebra of U0) holds (($1 = U1 & $2 = U2) implies $3 = ( U1 /\ U2 )));
A1: (for x,y being (Element of ( Sub U0 )) holds (ex z being (Element of ( Sub U0 )) st P[ x,y,z ]))
